---
permalink: "/gflexipack-standalone.html"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
noindex: true
---
{% import "partials/icons.njk" as icons %}
{% set ph = "data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" %}
{% set defaultStructures = ["PET / METPET / PE", "MATTE BOPP / METPET / PE", "PET / PE", "BOPA / PE", "PET / Alu / PE", "PET / Alu / BOPA / PE", "PE / PE", "Alox PET / PE"] %}
{% set lamTags = {
  "PET / METPET / PE": "High barrier",
  "MATTE BOPP / METPET / PE": "High · matte",
  "PET / PE": "Everyday",
  "BOPA / PE": "Puncture-resist",
  "PET / Alu / PE": "Ultra barrier",
  "PET / Alu / BOPA / PE": "Max barrier",
  "PE / PE": "Economical",
  "Alox PET / PE": "Clear barrier",
  "MDOPE / PE": "Recyclable",
  "BOPA / PE (nylon-PE)": "Puncture-resist",
  "High-clarity PA / PE": "High clarity",
  "PET / Alu / CPP": "Retort-grade",
  "PET / BOPA / Alu / CPP": "Retort · tough",
  "PET / Nylon / CPP (transparent retort)": "Transparent"
} %}
{% set arcMid = { "3": [26, 34, 26], "4": [20, 33, 33, 20], "5": [16, 28, 34, 28, 16], "9": [8, 19, 28, 35, 38, 35, 28, 19, 8] } %}
{% set arcRise = { "3": [10, 20, 28], "4": [8, 15, 22, 27], "5": [8, 16, 22, 26, 28] } %}
{% set arcFall = { "3": [22, 14, 6], "4": [24, 18, 11, 5], "5": [26, 21, 15, 9, 4] } %}
{% macro img(name, alt, cls) %}<img{% if cls %} class="{{ cls }}"{% endif %} data-img="{{ name }}" src="{{ ph }}" alt="{{ alt }}" loading="lazy" />{% endmacro %}
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>G Flexipack — Flexible Packaging Manufacturer · Bharuch, India</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 32 32'%3E%3Crect width='32' height='32' rx='6' fill='%233b2a20'/%3E%3Ctext x='16' y='22' font-family='Georgia,serif' font-size='18' fill='%23f4efe7' text-anchor='middle'%3EG%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
{{ "src/assets/css/styles.css" | inlineFile | safe }}
  </style>
  <style>
    /* SPA overrides: views + always-visible reveal (IO won't fire in hidden views) */
    [data-reveal] { opacity: 1 !important; transform: none !important; transition: none !important; }
    .view { display: none; }
    .view.is-active { display: block; }
    .nav-links a.is-current { opacity: 1; }
    .nav-links a.is-current::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
  </style>
</head>
<body id="top">

  <!-- NAV -->
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#/" aria-label="G Flexipack, home">{{ img("logo", "G Flexipack") }}</a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="#/about" data-nav="/about">About</a>
        <a href="#/products" data-nav="/products">Products</a>
        <a href="#/industries" data-nav="/industries">Industries</a>
        <a href="#/quality" data-nav="/quality">Quality</a>
        <a href="#/infrastructure" data-nav="/infrastructure">Infrastructure</a>
      </nav>
      <div class="nav-actions" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px;">
        <a class="nav-cta nav-cta-secondary" href="#/inquiry" style="border-color:transparent; background:transparent; padding:10px 4px;">Talk to a packaging expert</a>
        <a class="nav-cta" href="#/inquiry">Get a quote <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-progress" id="navProgress" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </header>

  <!-- ============================================================ HOME ============================================================ -->
  <main class="view is-active" data-route="/" data-title="G Flexipack — Flexible Packaging Manufacturer · Bharuch, India">
    <section class="hh-hero" id="hero">
      <div class="hh-hero-inner">
        <div class="hh-hero-text">
          <p class="hh-eyebrow">Flexible packaging · Est. {{ site.founded }}</p>
          <h1 class="hh-hero-title">Packaging built for <em>shelf impact.</em></h1>
          <p class="hh-hero-sub">G Flexipack is a flexible packaging manufacturer in Bharuch, Gujarat — custom-printed pouches for food, beverage, pharma, agrochemical and industrial brands. Fourteen formats, printed, laminated and converted under one roof.</p>
          <div class="hh-hero-ctas">
            <a class="cta cta-primary" href="#/inquiry">Get a quote <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hh-marquee" aria-label="Formats we print and sectors we pack for">
          <div class="hh-col"><div class="hh-track hh-down">
            {% for p in products %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:#3b2a20; --bandc:#eae0cd; --band-text:#3b2a20;">{{ img(p.image, p.name, "hh-photo") }}<span class="hh-tag">{{ p.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}{% for p in products %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:#3b2a20; --bandc:#eae0cd; --band-text:#3b2a20;">{{ img(p.image, p.name, "hh-photo") }}<span class="hh-tag">{{ p.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}
          </div></div>
          <div class="hh-col"><div class="hh-track hh-up">
            {% for s in industries %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:{{ s.accent }}; --bandc:#3b2a20; --band-text:#eae0cd;">{{ img(s.image, s.short + " sector packaging", "hh-photo") }}<span class="hh-tag">{{ s.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}{% for s in industries %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:{{ s.accent }}; --bandc:#3b2a20; --band-text:#eae0cd;">{{ img(s.image, s.short + " sector packaging", "hh-photo") }}<span class="hh-tag">{{ s.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}
          </div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hh-meta" aria-label="At a glance">
      <div><strong>ISO <em>Certified</em>.</strong> 9001:2015 quality management system, audited across every stage of production.</div>
      <div><strong><em>300+ MT</em> capacity.</strong> Printing, lamination and pouching lines running at scale, in-house.</div>
      <div><strong>Exporting to <em>10+ countries</em>.</strong> Sea freight coordinated worldwide, with full export documentation.</div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec welcome" id="about-teaser">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Welcome to our company</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title">Quality packaging, <em>since {{ site.founded }}.</em></h2>
        <p class="sec-lead">G Flexipack is a Bharuch-based flexible packaging manufacturer producing custom-printed pouches for food, beverage, pharma, personal care, agrochemical, industrial and household brands — 14 formats, printed, laminated and converted under one roof.</p>
        <p style="text-align:center; margin-top:26px;"><a class="cta cta-ghost" href="#/about">More about us <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec vm" aria-label="Vision and mission">
      <div class="vm-grid">
        <div class="vm-panel" style="--vc:#b25c2e;"><span class="vm-label">Our Vision</span><p class="vm-quote">To be the flexible packaging <em>partner of choice</em> for brands that care how their product lands on shelf.</p></div>
        <div class="vm-panel" style="--vc:#7a6e3f;"><span class="vm-label">Our Mission</span><p class="vm-quote">Design and print custom pouches that <em>protect the product</em> and represent the brand.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="ticker" aria-hidden="true"><div class="ticker-track">
      {% for i in [1,2] %}<div class="ticker-set">
        <span class="ticker-item">Upto <em>9-colour</em> printing</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">Food-grade <em>barrier films</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">ISO <em>9001:2015</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item"><em>300+ metric ton</em> capacity</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item"><em>60,000+ sq ft</em> climate-controlled plant</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">Exporting to <em>10+ countries</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
      </div>{% endfor %}
    </div></div>

    <section id="products-teaser">
      <div class="sec">
        <div class="sec-head">
          <p class="sec-eyebrow">Our products</p>
          <h2 class="sec-title">One roof, <em>every format.</em></h2>
          <p class="sec-lead">Custom dimensions, laminate structures, barrier levels and full-colour rotogravure print — all produced in-house.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rail-wrap">
        <div class="rail" id="formatRail">
          {% for p in products %}<a class="r-card" href="#/products/{{ p.slug }}">
            <span class="r-fig" style="--tbg:{{ p.tbg }};">{{ img(p.image, p.name) }}</span>
            <span class="r-body"><span class="r-name">{{ p.name }}</span><span class="r-link">View details →</span></span>
          </a>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <div class="rail-btns">
          <button class="rail-btn" id="railPrev" aria-label="Previous formats"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 5 8 12 15 19"></polyline></svg></button>
          <button class="rail-btn" id="railNext" aria-label="Next formats"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 5 16 12 9 19"></polyline></svg></button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rail-nav">
        <span class="rail-hint hint-desktop">Drag, or use the arrows</span>
        <span class="rail-hint hint-mobile">Swipe to explore →</span>
        <div class="rail-progress">
          <div class="rail-track"><div class="rail-fill" id="railFill"></div></div>
          <span class="rail-count"><em id="railCurrent">01</em> / {{ products | length }}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="height: 40px;"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="industries" id="industries-teaser">
      <div class="sec">
        <div class="sec-head">
          <p class="sec-eyebrow">Industries we serve</p>
          <h2 class="sec-title">The sector changes. <em>The standard doesn't.</em></h2>
          <p class="sec-lead">The hygiene, barrier and documentation adapt to the sector. The print quality doesn't.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="acc" id="indAcc">
          {% for s in industries %}<div class="acc-panel{% if loop.first %} is-open{% endif %}" style="--ic:{{ s.accent }};">
            {{ img(s.image, s.name + " sector packaging", "acc-photo") }}
            <div class="acc-photo-scrim"></div>
            <div class="acc-closed"><span class="acc-name-v">{{ s.short }}</span></div>
            <div class="acc-open"><h3>{{ s.name }}</h3><p>{{ s.applications | join(' · ') }}.</p><a class="r-link" href="#/industries/{{ s.slug }}">Explore sector →</a></div>
          </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <p class="shelf-hint hint-desktop">Hover a sector to open it</p>
        <p class="shelf-hint hint-mobile">Tap a sector to open it</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec" id="infrastructure">
      <div class="sec-head"><p class="sec-eyebrow">Infrastructure</p><h2 class="sec-title">60,000+ sq ft in <em>Bharuch, Gujarat.</em></h2><p class="sec-lead">Print, lamination, slitting and pouching — every step in-house.</p></div>
      <div class="infra-split">
        <a class="infra-photo-link" href="#/infrastructure" aria-label="See the full production line and specifications">
          <figure class="infra-photo">{{ img("printing-machine", "9-colour rotogravure printing press at the G Flexipack plant in Bharuch, Gujarat") }}</figure>
          <span class="infra-photo-cap"><span>See the full line &amp; specs</span><span class="arrow">→</span></span>
        </a>
        <div class="infra-copy">
          <p class="infra-lead">G Flexipack runs the full flexible-packaging line under one 60,000+ sq ft roof in Bharuch, Gujarat — producing 300+ MT a month. 9-colour rotogravure printing, solvent-less &amp; solvent-based lamination, precision slitting and in-house pouching, all ISO 9001:2015 certified and ASTM-tested before dispatch.</p>
          <p class="infra-caps">Rotogravure printing<span class="sep">·</span>Lamination<span class="sep">·</span>Slitting<span class="sep">·</span>Pouching</p>
          <a class="r-link infra-link" href="#/infrastructure">Inside our plant →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec" id="why-us">
      <div class="sec-head"><p class="sec-eyebrow">Why us</p><h2 class="sec-title">What sets us <em>apart.</em></h2><p class="sec-lead">Six reasons brands stay with us past the first order.</p></div>
      <div class="why-grid stagger">
        <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#b25c2e;"><span class="why-glyph">i</span><h4>Assured Quality</h4><p>ISO 9001:2015 systems and an in-house ASTM lab — eight tests on every batch, full documentation at dispatch.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#c89a3a;"><span class="why-glyph">ii</span><h4>On-Time Delivery</h4><p>3–5 week production lead times, honestly quoted and tracked — exporting to 10+ countries via sea freight.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#7a6e3f;"><span class="why-glyph">iii</span><h4>Customized Solutions</h4><p>Structure, size, barrier and finish engineered per product — recommendation within 24 hours of your brief.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#7a8a6c;"><span class="why-glyph">iv</span><h4>Advanced Machinery</h4><p>9-colour rotogravure with auto registration, solvent-less lamination, precision slitting and pouching lines.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#3b2a20;"><span class="why-glyph">v</span><h4>Skilled Workforce</h4><p>An experienced production and QC team under the Gangamani group's 20+ years of manufacturing discipline.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#b25c2e;"><span class="why-glyph">vi</span><h4>100% Recyclable Options</h4><p>Mono-material LLDPE structures for EPR-compliant brands — sustainability without sacrificing shelf appeal.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="clientele" aria-label="Our clientele">
      <div class="sec">
        <div class="sec-head"><p class="sec-eyebrow">Our clientele</p><h2 class="sec-title">Trusted across sectors <em>and borders.</em></h2></div>
        <div class="client-marquee"><div class="client-track">
          {% for i in [1,2] %}<div class="client-set"{% if i == 2 %} aria-hidden="true"{% endif %}>
            {% for c in clients %}{% if c.text %}<span class="client-badge client-badge-text"><b>{{ c.text }}</b></span>{% else %}<span class="client-badge"><img src="{{ ('src/assets/images/clients/' + c.img + '.webp') | dataUri }}" alt="{{ c.name }} logo" loading="lazy" /></span>{% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>{% endfor %}
        </div></div>
        <p class="client-note">Trusted by 200+ Indian brands across agrochemical, food, pharma and FMCG — a few of the names we pack for.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ TESTIMONIALS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" aria-label="Testimonials">
      <div class="sec-head"><p class="sec-eyebrow">What clients say</p><h2 class="sec-title">Trusted by brands <em>who don't compromise.</em></h2></div>
      <div class="testi-grid">
        <div class="testi-card"><p class="testi-quote">G Flexipack turned our first pouch order around faster than any supplier we'd worked with — and the print quality matched our brand exactly.</p><p class="testi-who"><b>Procurement Lead</b> · Agrochemical brand</p></div>
        <div class="testi-card"><p class="testi-quote">Their team recommended a barrier structure we hadn't considered, and it solved a shelf-life issue we'd been stuck on for months.</p><p class="testi-who"><b>Operations Head</b> · Food &amp; snacks brand</p></div>
        <div class="testi-card"><p class="testi-quote">Reliable lead times, clear communication, and documentation on every batch — exactly what we need for a regulated product.</p><p class="testi-who"><b>Quality Manager</b> · Pharma packer</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {% include "partials/inquiry-form.njk" %}
  </main>

  <!-- ============================================================ INFRASTRUCTURE ============================================================ -->
  <main class="view" data-route="/infrastructure" data-title="Infrastructure & Machinery — Rotogravure, Lamination, Slitting, Pouching | G Flexipack">
    <section class="sec" style="padding-bottom:24px;">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <p class="pp-crumbs" style="text-align:center;"><a href="#/">Home</a><span>/</span>Infrastructure</p>
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Infrastructure</p>
        <h1 class="sec-title" style="margin:0 auto 20px;">One factory floor, <em>zero handoffs.</em></h1>
        <p class="pp-intro" style="margin:0 auto;">Most converters outsource at least one stage — printing at one vendor, lamination at another. We don't. Every roll that enters our Bharuch facility as plain film leaves it as a finished, inspected pouch, on the same floor, under the same quality system.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pp-glance-inner" style="max-width:1000px; margin:32px auto 0;">
        <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Capacity</span><span class="pp-g-v">{{ site.capacity }}</span></div>
        <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Plant size</span><span class="pp-g-v">{{ site.plantSize }}</span></div>
        <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Formats</span><span class="pp-g-v">{{ products | length }} <i>pouch styles</i></span></div>
        <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Certification</span><span class="pp-g-v">{{ site.certs[0] }}</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ PROCESS FLOW ============ -->
    <section class="sec" style="padding-top:8px; padding-bottom:8px;">
      <div style="max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0; padding:0 20px;">
        <span class="pp-chip">01 · Film unwind</span><span style="color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0 8px;">→</span>
        <span class="pp-chip">02 · Rotogravure print</span><span style="color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0 8px;">→</span>
        <span class="pp-chip">03 · Lamination</span><span style="color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0 8px;">→</span>
        <span class="pp-chip">04 · Slitting</span><span style="color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0 8px;">→</span>
        <span class="pp-chip">05 · Pouching &amp; sealing</span><span style="color:var(--ink-soft); margin:0 8px;">→</span>
        <a class="pp-chip is-qc" href="#/quality">06 · QC &amp; dispatch <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ STAGE 02 · ROTOGRAVURE ============ -->
    <section class="pp-dark"><div class="sec">
      <div class="mach-row">
        <figure class="mach-photo" style="margin:0;">{{ img("printing-machine", "Rotogravure printing press") }}</figure>
        <div class="mach-text">
          <h2 class="sec-title" style="text-align:left;">Rotogravure <em>printing press.</em></h2>
          <p class="sec-lead" style="text-align:left; margin:14px 0 22px;">9-colour rotogravure with automatic registration control — sharp detail and consistent shade-matching, run after run. Cylinders are engraved per job, so repeat orders reprint to the same shade months later, not just within a single run. Every printed roll is inline-inspected before it moves to lamination, catching registration drift or colour variance before it compounds downstream.</p>
          <div class="pp-glance-inner" style="padding:0; margin-bottom:22px; justify-content:flex-start; gap:28px 40px;">
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Colours</span><span class="pp-g-v">9-colour</span></div>
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Max web width</span><span class="pp-g-v">1,000mm</span></div>
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Print speed</span><span class="pp-g-v">Up to 250 m/min</span></div>
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Registration</span><span class="pp-g-v">Automatic</span></div>
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Substrates</span><span class="pp-g-v">BOPP, PET, PE, metalised film</span></div>
          </div>
          <p style="margin:0; font-size:14px; color:var(--cream-soft); line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:var(--pale-gold);">What this means for your order:</strong> the shade you approve on the first run is the shade you get on the fiftieth — no re-matching, no drift batch to batch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div></section>

    <!-- ============ STAGE 03 · LAMINATION ============ -->
    <section class="sec">
      <div class="mach-row mach-row-rev">
        <figure class="mach-photo" style="margin:0;">{{ img("lami", "Solvent-less lamination machine") }}</figure>
        <div class="mach-text">
          <h2 class="sec-title" style="text-align:left;">Solvent-less &amp; solvent-based <em>lamination.</em></h2>
          <p class="sec-lead" style="text-align:left; margin:14px 0 22px;">Food-safe multi-layer bonding — the barrier structure is matched to what's going inside the pouch, not a one-size-fits-all laminate. Solvent-less bonding is our standard for food-contact layers, avoiding residual solvent entirely, while solvent-based lamination is available where a structure calls for it — retort-grade adhesion or specific barrier films, for example.</p>
          <div class="pp-glance-inner" style="padding:0; margin-bottom:22px; justify-content:flex-start; gap:28px 40px;">
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Bonding type</span><span class="pp-g-v">Solvent-less &amp; solvent-based</span></div>
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Max web width</span><span class="pp-g-v">1,000mm</span></div>
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Line speed</span><span class="pp-g-v">Up to 400 m/min</span></div>
            <div class="pp-g-item"><span class="pp-g-k">Structures</span><span class="pp-g-v">2–3 ply laminates</span></div>
          </div>
          <p style="margin:0; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.6;"><strong style="color:var(--ink);">What this means for your order:</strong> solvent-less as standard keeps residual solvent off food-contact layers, with solvent-based available for structures that need it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ STAGE 04 · SLITTING ============ -->
    <section class="pp-dark"><div class="sec">
      <div class="mach-row">
        <figure class="mach-photo" style="margin:0;">{{ img("slitting-machine", "Slitting machine") }}</figure>
        <div class="mach-text">
          <h2 class="sec-title" style="text-align:left;">Precision <em>slitting lines.</em></h2>
          <p class="sec-lead" style="text-align:left; margin:14px 0 22px;">Tension-controlled winding to exact reel widths — output either goes straight to pouching or ships as finished film rolls. Consistent tension across the reel prevents telescoping and wrinkling in transit, so what leaves our slitting line arrives at yours ready to run, not needing to be re-wound first.</p>
          <div class="pp-glance-inner" style="padding:0; margin-bottom:22px; justify-content:flex-start; gap:28px 40px;">
